hannel 4]]\n|10 September 2012\n|-\n|2012\n|''[[Hotel GB]]''\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|1 October 2012 \u2013 5 October 2012\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Gordon Ramsay's Home Cooking]]''\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|\n|-\n|2013\u2013present\n|''[[MasterChef Junior]]''\n|[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n|\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Ant & Dec's Saturday Night Takeaway]]''\n|[[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]\n|1 March 2013\n|-\n|2014\n|''Ramsay's Costa del Nightmares''\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|23 September 2014\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[MasterChef (Polish TV series)|Masterchef Poland]]''\n|[[TVN (Poland)|TVN]]\n|19 October 2014\n|-\n|2015\u2013present\n|''[[Matilda and the Ramsay Bunch]]''\n|[[CBBC]]\n|14 April 2015 \u2013 present. ''Gordon is also an executive producer.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/cbbc/shows/matilda-and-the-ramsay-bunch|title=Matilda and the Ramsay Bunch - CBBC|publisher=BBC|accessdate=7 December 2017}}</ref>''\n|-\n|2017\n|[[The F Word (U.S. TV series)|''The F Word US'']] \n|[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[The Nightly Show (UK TV series)|The Nightly Show]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/presscentre/press-releases/gordon-ramsay-returns-uks-most-watched-commercial-channel|title=Gordon Ramsay returns to the UK\u2019s most watched commercial channel|website=itv.com|publisher=ITV Press Centre|accessdate=18 February 2017}}</ref>''\n|[[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Culinary Genius (TV series)|Culinary Genius]]''\n|[[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''Gordon Ramsay on Cocaine''\n|[[ITV (TV network)|ITV]]\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Mickey and the Roadster Racers]]''\n|[[Disney Junior]]\n|5 November 2017. ''Episode: \"Diner Dog Rescue\"''\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Please Take Care of My Refrigerator]]''\n|[[JTBC]]\n|11 December 2017\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Gordon Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell & Back]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fox.com/gordon-ramsays-24-hours-to-hell-back/|title=24 Hours To Hell & Back|website=Fox.com|publisher=Fox Broadcasting Company|accessdate=29 March 2018}}</ref>''\n